Suppose I create a widget:
        # Create a widget to hold the layout
        self.layout_widget = QtWidgets.QWidget(self)

And then I create a vertical layout:
        # Create a vertical layout for the widget
        layout = QtWidgets.QVBoxLayout(self.layout_widget)

Two containers will be added to the vertical
        container1 = QtWidgets.QWidget()
        h1 = QtWidgets.QHBoxLayout(container1)
        layout.addWidget(container1)

        container2 = QtWidgets.QWidget()
        h1 = QtWidgets.QHBoxLayout(container2)
        layout.addWidget(container2)


is there a way to toggle between removing container2 and then adding again? 